      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Ordinary year (365d) → 1 odd day\nLeap year (366d)     → 2 odd days\n\nCentury odd days:\n100 yrs → 5    200 yrs → 3\n300 yrs → 1    400 yrs → 0\n\nPattern repeats: 0, 5, 3, 1\n(for 400, 100, 200, 300)",
      "autoResize": true,
