    {
      "id": "el_25",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 672,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Apply decision tree\n  ÷4? → ÷100? → ÷400?\n  1600: /4Y /100Y /400Y → LEAP\n  1700: /4Y /100Y /400N → ORDINARY\n  1900: /4Y /100Y /400N → ORDINARY\n  2000: /4Y /100Y /400Y → LEAP\n  2024: /4Y /100N → LEAP\n\nTRICK:\nCentury years: must ÷400\nOther years: just ÷4\n1600✓ 1700✗ 1800✗ 1900✗ 2000✓\n\nAnswer: 1600, 2000, 2024 = Leap ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
