    {
      "id": "el_35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1038,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Ordinary = 365/7 = 52w+1 → 1\nStep 2: Leap = 366/7 = 52w+2 → 2\n  2023 → ordinary → 1 odd day\n  2024 → leap → 2 odd days\n\nTRICK:\nOrdinary year = 1, Leap year = 2\nAlways! No calculation needed.\nJan 1 shifts by 1 (ord) or 2 (leap)\n\nAnswer: 2023=1, 2024=2 odd days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3500,
      "version": 1,
