      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Ordinary = 365/7 = 52w+1 → 1\nStep 2: Leap = 366/7 = 52w+2 → 2\n  2023 → ordinary → 1 odd day\n  2024 → leap → 2 odd days\n\nTRICK:\nOrdinary year = 1, Leap year = 2\nAlways! No calculation needed.\nJan 1 shifts by 1 (ord) or 2 (leap)\n\nAnswer: 2023=1, 2024=2 odd days ✓",
