      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 100yr = 76ord+24leap\n  = 76+48 = 124, 124%7 = 5\nStep 2: 200yr=10%7=3, 300yr=15%7=1\n  400yr=20%7=6+extra leap=0\n\nTRICK:\nMemorize: 100→5, 200→3, 300→1, 400→0\nPattern repeats every 400 years\n400yr = 0 → calendar repeats!\n\nAnswer: 300yrs=1, 400yrs=0 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
