      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1038,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Wed=3, 65%7 = 2 odd days\nStep 2: Past → subtract: 3-2 = 1\n  1 = Monday\n\nTRICK:\nPast: day_code - odd_days (mod 7)\nFuture: day_code + odd_days (mod 7)\n65 ago: 3-2=1=Mon\n45 ahead: 3+3=6=Sat (45%7=3)\n\nAnswer: 65 ago = Monday ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
