      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Century: 1600→0, 300→1\nStep 2: Years 1901-1946 (46yr)\n  Leap=11, Ord=35 → 35+22=57%7=1\nStep 3: Months Jan-Jul: 3+0+3+2+3+2+3=16%7=2\nStep 4: Day: 15%7=1\n  Total = 1+1+2+1 = 5\n\nTRICK:\n5 = Friday (0=Sun...6=Sat)\nSame method every time!\n\nAnswer: Friday ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
