    {
      "id": "el_55",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1361,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Leap years: 2004,2008,...,2096\nStep 2: Count = (2096-2004)/4 + 1 = 24\n  Is 2100 leap? /4Y /100Y /400N → NO\n\nTRICK:\nCount multiples of 4 in range\nRemove century years not ÷400\n2004 to 2096: (96-4)/4+1 = 24\n2100 excluded → still 24\n\nAnswer: 24 times ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
