      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Leap years: 2004,2008,...,2096\nStep 2: Count = (2096-2004)/4 + 1 = 24\n  Is 2100 leap? /4Y /100Y /400N → NO\n\nTRICK:\nCount multiples of 4 in range\nRemove century years not ÷400\n2004 to 2096: (96-4)/4+1 = 24\n2100 excluded → still 24\n\nAnswer: 24 times ✓",
