      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Wed=3, Fri=5, gap=2\n  First Fri = Mar 1+2 = Mar 3\nStep 2: Then +7 each: 3,10,17,24,31\n\nTRICK:\nGap = target - known day code\nIf gap<0: add 7\nFirst = known_date + gap\nThen every +7 until month ends\n\nAnswer: 3, 10, 17, 24, 31 ✓",
