      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Count odd days from 2017:\n  2017(1) 2018(1) 2019(1) 2020(2)\n  2021(1) 2022(1) → sum=7%7=0\nStep 2: 2023 ordinary + sum=0 → MATCH!\n\nTRICK:\nOrdinary repeats: +6, +11, +11\nLeap repeats: every 28 years\n2017(ord)+6=2023 ✓\n\nAnswer: 2023 has same calendar ✓",
