      "width": 260,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Jan=31 days = 4w+3 extra\n  Extra days: 29th,30th,31st\nStep 2: Jan 1=Sun → 29=Sun\n  Sundays: 1,8,15,22,29 = 5\n\nTRICK:\n31-day month: 3 days appear 5×\n30-day month: 2 days appear 5×\n28-day month: all days appear 4×\nFirst day + next 2 get 5 appearances\n\nAnswer: 5 Sundays in January ✓",
